CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: STAK Inc. is a fast-growing company specializing in the research, development, manufacturing, and sale of oilfield-specialized production and maintenance equipment. We design and manufacture oilfield-specialized production and maintenance equipment, then collaborate with qualified specialized vehicle manufacturing companies to integrate the equipment onto vehicle chassis, producing specialized oilfield vehicles for sale. Additionally, we sell oilfield-specialized equipment components, related products, and provide automation solutions.
